{"tid":815783,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"銀魂在週刊少年Jump上的最終話 中文情報,空知英秋猩猩謝罪信的內容：","createTime":"2018-09-12T09:57:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T09:55:24.000Z","uid":3020,"like":92,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"fb441454c502b50bb12b0f4176a047c5a20af5f8","tid":815783,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T09:57:12.000Z","msg":"最終話內容：依然還在和天道眾殘存黨對抗中。最後一頁銀桑說了&ldquo;我們的戰爭將在JUMP GIGA繼續下去！！！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n猩猩謝罪信內容：基本上就是和讀者道歉說自己之前說了會在8月讓銀魂完結但依然拖到了現在，而即使畫到了這所謂的&ldquo;最終話&rdquo;也無法好好地填完坑完結。還有這並不是大家所想像的那樣被JUMP催趕才草草完結這最後一話。 JUMP也提議了&ldquo;既然沒法在指定時間內好好完結那就在GIGA上繼續吧&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下一話將在12月的GIGA和大家見面。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n還有配合漫畫完結將會舉辦最後一次的人氣投票。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年將會有另一個銀魂祭（聲優見面會那個）。"},{"pid":"fd571dd6312ce2d06f5264d0877a81353919c745","tid":815783,"uid":4917,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T09:59:36.000Z","msg":"點解要逼佢完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2eea6af70a735a0fc75ad945794c5ef2dc68f49","tid":815783,"uid":31151,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:01:24.000Z","msg":"不如唔好完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f449cf7bebdfaa71a950f1cf27036bbc7c1d4fef","tid":815783,"uid":190789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:03:36.000Z","msg":"Jump同作者成日都達唔到一致意見"},{"pid":"c758502a3dfd8224b5a1f9676d030894bb0510a6","tid":815783,"uid":20554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:04:01.000Z","msg":"姐係未完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160dc70e239672a1595d70288ae68455b39b224e","tid":815783,"uid":10890,"like":93,"dislike":0,"score":93,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:06:22.000Z","msg":"即係又係完結欺詐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/do